Package: TIE
Type: Package
Title: Estimating tail index in time series
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Buyu Lin
Maintainer: The package maintainer <lbywhj@mail.ustc.edu.cn>
Imports:
    neldermead,
    stats,
    quantmod,
    SpatialExtremes,
    Ball,
    DAAG,
    MASS,
    RANN,
    boot,
    bootstrap,
    energy,
    microbenchmark
Description: Use a new method to estimate the tail index, combine the quantile regression and 
    extreme value theory. I adapt the framework of Tail Index Regression to the time series,
    especially in the financial time seires. And make some improvement of the original framework,
    and use the method to estimate very high quantiles. 
